'''妮莉·金·費塔朵'''（Nelly Kim Furtado，{{bd|1978年|12月2日|||catIdx=F}}）是一位[[加拿大|加拿大]][[女歌手|女歌手]]、[[詞曲作家|詞曲作家]]、[[演員|演員]]。 

妮莉·費塔朵以她2000年發行的《[[哇!妮莉|哇!妮莉]]》（''Whoa, Nelly!''）一舉成名，其中收錄了她獲[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]最佳流行女歌手獎的單曲《I'm like a Bird》。2003年發行了《[[故事書_(专辑)|故事書]]》（''Folklore''）這張市場反應不佳的專輯之後，她以2006年發行的《[[解放_(专辑)|解放]]》（''Loose''）和專輯中的熱門單曲，包括《愛趴》（''Promiscuous''）、《少男殺手》（''Maneater''）、《好好說》（''Say It Right''）與《好景不常》（''[[All_Good_Things|All Good Things]] (Come to an End)''），而再度受到矚目。時至今日，她已在全球銷售了1500萬張專輯（截至2007年4月）。2012年9月推出專輯，The Spirit Indestructible。妮莉在2017年3月推出新專輯，THE RIDE。

妮莉·費塔朵以大膽嘗試不同的[[樂器|樂器]]、音效、[[曲風|曲風]]、[[語言|語言]]还有唱腔聞名，因為她受到了多樣的音樂口味與對不同文化的興趣影響<ref name=ym>{{cite web|url=http://music.yahoo.com/read/interview/12058557|title=Exclusive LAUNCH Artist Chat|work=Yahoo! Music|accessdate=28 May 2006|archive-date=2006-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061217112152/http://music.yahoo.com/read/interview/12058557|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=mm>{{cite web|url=http://www.maplemusic.com/artists/nfu/bio.asp|title=Nelly Furtado Biography|work=MapleMusic|accessdate=27 May 2006|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111123100037/http://www.maplemusic.com/artists/nfu/bio.asp|archive-date=2011-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==個人生平==
===早年生活===  

妮莉·費塔朵出生於[[英屬哥倫比亞|英屬哥倫比亞]][[維多利亞|維多利亞]]的一个[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]移民家庭，雙親各為Maria Manuela與António José Furtado。<ref name=rsjan01>{{cite web| url=http://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/5918613/furtado_goes_portuguese/| title=Furtado Goes Portuguese| work=Rolling Stone| accessdate=27 May 2006| archive-date=2007-06-25| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070625045453/http://www.rollingstone.com/news/story/5918613/furtado_goes_portuguese/| dead-url=yes}}</ref> 她的名字是來自於[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]的體操選手Nellie Kim（涅利·金）。<ref name=ym/> 妮莉在四歲時在教堂的[[葡萄牙日|葡萄牙日]]上首次與媽媽共同獻唱。Although remaining unclear about her religious beliefs, she still affirms a belief in God, the Ten Commandments, and in avoiding the [[Seven_Sins|Seven Sins]].<ref name=ym/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/nellyfurtado/articles/story/5931858/fly_girl|title=Fly Girl|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2007-06-06|archive-date=2007-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070106054422/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/nellyfurtado/articles/story/5931858/fly_girl|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 9歲起逐漸開始接觸[[伸縮喇叭|伸縮喇叭]]、[[四弦琴|四弦琴]]，幾年後也開始學習[[吉他|吉他]]與[[鋼琴|鋼琴]]。12歲起，她開始寫歌，<ref name=ym/> 且開始在葡萄牙遊行樂隊中演奏。<ref name=rsjan01/>

Furtado has acknowledged her family as the source of her strong work ethic; she spent eight summers working as a [[chambermaid|chambermaid]] with her mother, who was a [[Housekeeper_(servant)|housekeeper]] in Victoria.<ref name=amg>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusicguide.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&sql=11:lcaxlfjekcqe~T1|title=Nelly Furtado Biography|work=All Music Guide|accessdate=27 May 2006}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> She has stated that coming from a working class background has shaped her identity in a positive way.<ref name=ym/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/nellyfurtado/articles/story/5931858/fly_girl|title=Fly Girl|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=16 Aug 2001|archive-date=2007-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070106054422/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/nellyfurtado/articles/story/5931858/fly_girl|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

與妮莉首次合作的音樂家是[[嘻哈音樂|Rapper]]與[[唱片騎師|DJ]]。<ref name=mtv>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/bands/f/furtado_nelly/qa_feature_060706/|title=How Nelly Furtado Got Her Ghetto Pass|work=MTV|accessdate=16 August 2006|last=Shepherd|first=Julianne|archive-date=2008-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411082519/http://www.mtv.com/bands/f/furtado_nelly/qa_feature_060706/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 高中二年級時在[[多倫多|多倫多]]遇到了[[嘻哈|嘻哈]]團體Crazy Cheese的團員Tallis Newkirk，她在他們的專輯「Join the Ranks」中擔任"Waitin' 4 the Streets"的主唱。<ref name=nelstar>Nelly also featured alongside Los Angeles-based Hip Hop group [[Jurassic_5|Jurassic 5]], in their single "Thin Line", from the album Power In Numbers.
{{cite web|url=http://www.nelstar-project.com/about/nelstar|title=Nelstar* (Nelly Furtado) Biography|work=Nelstar-Project.com|accessdate=9 December 2005|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060101212435/http://www.nelstar-project.com/about/nelstar/|archivedate=2006年1月1日}}</ref> 1996年從高中畢業後，她搬到了多倫多，並與Newkirk組成了一個Trip-hop團體Nelstar。最終，她認為Trip hop的曲風有過多種族隔離的意味，她也認為這樣的曲風不能代表她的個性，更無法突顯她的歌唱實力。<ref name=nelstar/> 因此，她離開了這個團體回到了家鄉。

然而，她在搬回家鄉之前，曾在1997年上過女性才藝節目Honey Jam表演。<ref name=nelstar/><ref name=honeyjam>{{cite web | url = http://www.chartattack.com/damn/2003/05/2705.cfm | title = Honey Jam Searches for Urban Women | work = ChartAttack | date = 2003-05-27 | accessdate =  | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930031700/http://www.chartattack.com/damn/2003/05/2705.cfm | archivedate = 2007-09-30 }}
